		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If in windowed mode: move the mouse cursor outside of the Nestopia window.
<br />
<br />If in full-screen mode: drag the mouse cursor to the far bottom right or bottom left of the screen.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


